        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 3 at 5:24PM PDT until June 3 at 6:00PM PDT by NWS Las Vegas NV</headline>
        <description>At 523 PM PDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Logandale, or 8
miles east of Moapa Town, moving north at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Overton, Moapa Town, Moapa Valley, and Logandale.

This includes Interstate 15 in Nevada between mile markers 91 and
101.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
